sequenceDiagram
    participant vLLM as vLLM Model Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP / Inference Scheduler
    participant Prom as Prometheus / Thanos Querier<br/>9090-9091/TCP HTTPS
    participant WVA as WVA Controller<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HPA as HPA / KEDA
    participant Deploy as Deployment / LWS

    Note over vLLM,Deploy: Flow 1: Saturation-Based Autoscaling

    vLLM->>Prom: Expose vLLM metrics<br/>(KV cache, queue depth, latency)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    WVA->>Prom: PromQL query<br/>(vllm:kv_cache_usage_perc,<br/>vllm:num_requests_waiting)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / Bearer Token
    Note over WVA: Saturation Engine V1/V2<br/>analyzes metrics, runs<br/>throughput + queueing analyzers
    WVA->>WVA: Emit wva_desired_replicas<br/>on /metrics endpoint
    Prom->>WVA: Scrape /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Bearer Token (TokenReview)
    HPA->>K8sAPI: Read external metric<br/>wva_desired_replicas<br/>(via prometheus-adapter or KEDA)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    HPA->>Deploy: Scale Deployment<br/>(scale subresource)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over vLLM,Deploy: Flow 2: Scale-from-Zero

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over EPP: Client request arrives<br/>at InferencePool with<br/>0 ready endpoints
        EPP->>Prom: Expose queue metric<br/>(inference_extension_flow_<br/>control_queue_size)
        WVA->>Prom: Query EPP queue depth<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / Bearer Token
        Note over WVA: Scale-from-Zero Engine<br/>detects pending requests<br/>for idle variant
        WVA->>K8sAPI: PATCH scale subresource<br/>(replicas: 0 → 1)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token (SA token)
        K8sAPI->>Deploy: Scale Deployment/LWS<br/>to 1 replica
    end
